JUST TO DRUM UP AN AUDIENCE

13:25.105 --> 13:27.205
FOR OUR 500TH SONDHEIM CONCERT.

13:27.240 --> 13:28.140
- I HAD A FEELING.

13:28.175 --> 13:30.875
- I WAS HOPING
THAT I WOULD FIND SOMEONE

13:30.911 --> 13:31.881
I COULD CONNECT TO.

13:31.912 --> 13:33.312
- SOMEONE APPROPRIATE.

13:33.346 --> 13:34.476
- EXACTLY.

13:34.514 --> 13:37.284
SOMEONE APPROPRIATE.

13:37.317 --> 13:39.447
- WELL...

13:39.486 --> 13:44.056
I SAY LET'S GET TO KNOW
EACH OTHER AND...

13:44.091 --> 13:46.061
SEE WHAT HAPPENS.

13:46.093 --> 13:47.063
- TAKE IT SLOW.

13:47.094 --> 13:50.064
I ALWAYS PREFERRED
ANDANTE TO PRESTO ANYWAY.

13:50.097 --> 13:51.127
[chuckles]

13:51.164 --> 13:52.974
- OKAY, BOYS...

13:53.000 --> 13:56.040
THESE'LL HELP COOL YOU DOWN.

13:59.506 --> 14:01.876
- 27 MINUTES ON MY NIPPLES--

14:01.909 --> 14:03.079
I CLOCKED IT.

14:03.110 --> 14:06.310
I MEAN, I EXPECTED HIM TO KNOW
WHAT TO DO WITH HIS HANDS,

14:06.346 --> 14:07.546
'CAUSE THAT'S HIS BUSINESS,

14:07.580 --> 14:11.250
BUT HE HAS
THE MOST TALENTED TONGUE.

14:11.284 --> 14:12.494
EVERY TIME I CAME--

14:12.519 --> 14:14.349
all:
"EVERY TIME"?

14:14.387 --> 14:18.227
- HE WOULD JUST
KEEP ON GOING...

14:18.258 --> 14:21.028
LICKING ME EVERYWHERE.

14:21.061 --> 14:22.901
- I ONCE KNEW A GUY
WHO COULD TIE A CHERRY STEM

14:22.930 --> 14:24.260
INTO A KNOT
WITH HIS TONGUE.

14:24.297 --> 14:26.167
I WAS AFRAID TO LET HIM
BLOW ME.

14:26.199 --> 14:27.299
- 27 MINUTES?

14:27.334 --> 14:30.904
WAS THAT 13 1/2
ON EACH NIPPLE, OR--

14:30.938 --> 14:34.168
- 16 RIGHT, 11 LEFT.

14:34.207 --> 14:36.977
- YEAH, THAT'S PROBABLY HOW LONG
IT TAKES HIM TO GET IT UP.

14:37.010 --> 14:38.150
- I WOULDN'T KNOW.

14:38.178 --> 14:39.978
I NEVER SAW IT
WHEN IT WAS DOWN.

14:40.013 --> 14:42.653
- ANOTHER VIAGRA SUCCESS STORY.

14:42.682 --> 14:44.522
- SO ARE YOU BRINGING HIM
TO WOODY'S TONIGHT?

14:44.551 --> 14:46.521
- HE'S NOT REALLY
INTO THE BAR SCENE.

14:46.553 --> 14:47.653
[weights clanging]

14:47.687 --> 14:49.417
- WELL, WHAT IS HE INTO?

14:49.456 --> 14:51.156
- HIS LIFE.

14:51.191 --> 14:52.531
- LIKE THE GUY I MET.

14:52.559 --> 14:54.659
- YOU MET SOMEONE?

14:54.694 --> 14:56.534
- HE'S VERY NICE,

14:56.563 --> 14:58.703
VERY INTELLIGENT,
VERY INTERESTING.

14:58.731 --> 15:01.031
- IS HE A TOP OR A BOTTOM?

15:01.068 --> 15:03.238
- YOU KNOW,
NOT EVERYBODY JUDGES PEOPLE

15:03.270 --> 15:04.270
BY YOUR CRITERIA, OKAY?

15:04.304 --> 15:05.974
ROGER AND I--
- [laughs]

15:06.006 --> 15:06.966
ROGER?

15:07.007 --> 15:08.637
- ROGER AND I HAVE DECIDED

15:08.675 --> 15:11.235
TO GET TO KNOW EACH OTHER
BEFORE WE HAVE SEX.

15:11.278 --> 15:14.648
- WHAT DO YOU THINK YOU ARE--
LESBIANS?

15:14.681 --> 15:16.621
- IT'S LIKE
THE MIRROR HAS TWO FACES.

15:16.649 --> 15:18.489
- NO. NO, IT IS,
BECAUSE BARBRA

15:18.518 --> 15:20.548
PLAYS AN UNATTRACTIVE
PROFESSOR--NO OFFENSE--

15:20.587 --> 15:21.517
WHO MARRIES JEFF BRIDGES

15:21.554 --> 15:23.094
BECAUSE NEITHER ONE OF THEM
CAN HANDLE SEX.

15:23.123 --> 15:25.163
BUT OF COURSE
BARBRA GETS HORNY BECAUSE,

15:25.192 --> 15:27.292
HELLO, JEFF'S
SUCH A DREAMBOAT.

15:27.327 --> 15:29.097
SO SHE HOPS ON A STAIRMASTER
FOR, LIKE, TWO MINUTES,

15:29.129 --> 15:30.159
EATS A CARROT STICK,
AND THEN, POOF!

15:30.197 --> 15:31.327
SHE'S GORGEOUS.

15:31.364 --> 15:34.274
THEN SHE COMES IN DRESSED
LIKE THE HOOKER IN NUTS,

15:34.301 --> 15:36.171
AND, OF COURSE,
JEFF'S WILLING TO FUCK HER.

15:36.203 --> 15:40.373
AND, UM,
THEY DANCE IN THE STREET.

15:40.407 --> 15:42.177
- AND SHE STILL
WASN'T NOMINATED.

15:42.209 --> 15:44.309
- YOU KNOW,
YOU DO IT RIGHT AWAY,

15:44.344 --> 15:47.184
OR YOU DON'T DO IT AT ALL.

15:47.214 --> 15:51.584
I'M HAPPY FOR YOU, MIKEY.

15:51.618 --> 15:54.318
- THE FUCK HE IS.

15:55.622 --> 15:58.462
- JUSTIN, DAPHNE'S HERE.

15:58.491 --> 16:01.331
MOLLY...
- WE'RE GOING TO BE LATE.

16:01.361 --> 16:03.531
HEY, LOOK...

16:03.563 --> 16:06.403
JUSTIN TOLD ME HOW GREAT
YOU'RE BEING ABOUT EVERYTHING.

16:06.433 --> 16:08.343
AND I JUST WANT TO SAY
I THINK HE'S REALLY LUCKY

16:08.368 --> 16:09.998
TO HAVE SUCH
AN UNDERSTANDING MOM.

16:10.037 --> 16:11.637
- WELL, I'M TRYING.

16:11.671 --> 16:13.211
- YEAH, WELL,
IT MUST BE HARD,

16:13.240 --> 16:15.180
'CAUSE MY FAMILY--
I'M BLACK,

16:15.208 --> 16:16.278
MY PARENTS ARE BLACK.

16:16.309 --> 16:18.549
WE'RE ALL BLACK,
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

16:18.578 --> 16:20.748
- I THINK SO.

16:20.780 --> 16:23.180
- OH.
DID YOU SEE THE FLYER?

16:23.216 --> 16:25.446
- WHAT FLYER?
- FOR THE ART SHOW.

16:25.485 --> 16:27.085
HIS NAME'S REALLY BIG.

16:27.120 --> 16:29.120
WOULD YOU COME ON ALREADY?

16:29.156 --> 16:32.056
- GAY AND LESBIAN CENT--
WHEN DID THIS HAPPEN?

16:32.092 --> 16:33.792
- OH, MY GOD.
YOU MEAN HE DIDN'T--

16:33.826 --> 16:35.796
- HE DOESN'T TELL ME MUCH
THESE DAYS.

16:35.828 --> 16:38.398
- OH, PROMISE
YOU WON'T TELL HIM I TOLD YOU,

16:38.431 --> 16:39.571
OR HE'LL STOP TELLING ME.

16:39.599 --> 16:41.229
- YOU DON'T HAVE TO YELL.

16:41.268 --> 16:43.638
I HEARD YOU THE FIRST TIME.

16:43.670 --> 16:45.770
AND I DON'T KNOW
WHEN I'LL BE BACK.

16:45.805 --> 16:47.235
- JUSTIN!

16:47.274 --> 16:49.144
