16:49.176 --> 16:50.806
BE CAREFUL.

16:50.843 --> 16:54.613
- CHRIS, PASS ME THAT HAMMER.

16:54.647 --> 16:56.117
- YOU'RE REALLY GOOD AT THAT.

16:56.149 --> 16:57.549
- THANKS.

16:57.584 --> 16:59.194
I LIKE YOU GUYS' BRACELETS.

16:59.219 --> 17:00.389
- OH, THEY'RE FOR FRIENDSHIP.

17:00.420 --> 17:02.260
I MEAN, HE'S NOT MY BOYFRIEND
OR ANYTHING.

17:02.289 --> 17:03.789
- I FIGURED.

17:03.823 --> 17:05.532
- YOU CAN TELL I'M GAY?

17:05.558 --> 17:08.428
- WELL, YOU'RE HERE,
AREN'T YOU?

17:08.461 --> 17:10.800
I'M HEADING ON DOWN TO THE DINER
TO GET A SODA.

17:10.829 --> 17:12.630
YOU WANT TO COME?

17:12.665 --> 17:15.065
- SURE.

17:15.102 --> 17:17.442
- WHAT--
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

17:17.470 --> 17:18.740
SHE THINKS YOU'RE A LESBIAN.

17:18.771 --> 17:21.570
- WELL, CAN'T I BE ONE
OF THE COOL PEOPLE TOO?

17:21.608 --> 17:22.738
- YOU'RE A FREAK.

17:22.775 --> 17:24.335
[chuckles]

17:26.346 --> 17:28.646
- YOU KNOW,
YOU HAVE REAL TALENT.

17:28.681 --> 17:30.681
- REALLY?
- YOU SHOULD DEVELOP IT--

17:30.717 --> 17:31.817
MAYBE GO TO ART SCHOOL.

17:31.851 --> 17:33.321
- I'VE BEEN THINKING
ABOUT THAT.

17:33.353 --> 17:34.723
- WELL, IF YOU EVER NEED
A RECOMMENDATION...

17:34.754 --> 17:37.164
- THANKS.

17:37.190 --> 17:40.860
- DO YOU THINK
BRIAN'S GOING TO COME?

17:40.893 --> 17:43.563
- DON'T EXPECT TOO MUCH
FROM HIM, OKAY?

17:43.596 --> 17:46.326
- WHAT'S TOO MUCH?

17:46.366 --> 17:47.866
- ANYTHING AT ALL.

17:47.900 --> 17:49.640
YOU'LL HAVE LOTS
OF RELATIONSHIPS, JUSTIN,

17:49.669 --> 17:51.799
WITH LOTS
OF INTERESTING PEOPLE.

17:51.838 --> 17:55.708
