AS I REMEMBER IT.

18:30.410 --> 18:33.150
EVEN THE GUYS LOOK THE SAME.

18:33.180 --> 18:34.610
- WHY'D YOU STOP?

18:34.647 --> 18:37.877
- IT WASN'T FOR ME.
AND I MET SOMEONE.

18:37.917 --> 18:39.317
- OH.

18:39.352 --> 18:41.822
- YEAH, WE WERE TOGETHER
ALMOST SIX YEARS.

18:41.854 --> 18:43.694
- WOW.

18:43.723 --> 18:46.893
