THE FAMOUS CHIROPRACTOR?

18:58.571 --> 19:00.641
- DAVID, THIS IS EMMETT.

19:00.673 --> 19:03.413
- HI, EMMETT.
- HELLO, GORGEOUS.

19:03.443 --> 19:06.483
SO, UM--
SO I'VE, UH--

19:06.513 --> 19:07.783
I'VE GOT A LITTLE TIGHTNESS
RIGHT IN HERE--

19:07.814 --> 19:08.784
ONE PLACE I DON'T NEED IT.

19:08.815 --> 19:09.875
[chuckles]
WOULD YOU MIND?

19:09.916 --> 19:12.286
- I WOULDN'T MIND AT ALL
IF YOU MADE AN APPOINTMENT.

19:12.319 --> 19:14.719
- WELL, IT'S WORTH A SHOT.

19:14.754 --> 19:16.224
- WHERE'S TED?

19:16.256 --> 19:18.626
- OUT WITH
THE PILLSBURY DOUGHBOY.

19:18.658 --> 19:19.928
OH, MY GOD.

19:19.959 --> 19:21.489
THAT GUY OVER THERE LOOKS
EXACTLY

19:21.528 --> 19:23.528
LIKE MATTHEW MCCONAUGHEY.

19:23.563 --> 19:27.533
MAYBE HE SMOKES POT NAKED.
EXCUSE ME.

19:27.567 --> 19:28.637
- [laughs]

19:28.668 --> 19:30.398
HE DOESN'T HOLD
ANYTHING BACK, HUH?

19:30.437 --> 19:34.867
- HE WAS TONING IT DOWN
FOR YOU.

19:38.445 --> 19:41.405
- WHERE THE FUCK
HAVE YOU BEEN?

19:41.448 --> 19:43.378
- BRIAN, THIS IS DAVID.

19:43.416 --> 19:45.286
- OH, FUCK ME,
THE NEW BEAU.

19:45.318 --> 19:46.818
- I'VE HEARD A LOT ABOUT YOU.

19:46.853 --> 19:48.593
- AND I'VE HEARD
A LOT ABOUT YOU TOO.

19:48.621 --> 19:52.761
- 16 RIGHT, 11 LEFT.

19:52.792 --> 19:54.562
- EXCUSE ME?
- NOTHING.

19:54.594 --> 19:56.764
