WHAT ARE YOU ON?

19:56.796 --> 19:58.766
- OH, "E," "K," GHB--

19:58.798 --> 20:00.768
MOST OF THE LETTERS
ON SESAME STREET.

20:00.800 --> 20:02.470
- YOU'RE GOING TO GET DEHYDRATED
TAKING ALL THAT SHIT.

20:02.502 --> 20:03.872
I'M GOING TO GET YOU
SOME WATER.

20:03.903 --> 20:06.413
WANT A BEER?
- SURE.

20:09.742 --> 20:11.712
