20:15.748 --> 20:18.818
SO, DOC...

20:18.851 --> 20:22.461
DO YOU FUCK
ALL OF YOUR PATIENTS?

20:22.489 --> 20:24.489
- WELL, IF YOU'RE REFERRING
TO MICHAEL,

20:24.524 --> 20:29.304
I RELEASED HIM FROM MY CARE
BEFORE WE WENT OUT TOGETHER.

20:29.329 --> 20:30.429
[clears throat]

20:30.463 --> 20:32.733
WHAT ABOUT YOU?
