20:32.765 --> 20:34.395
- ADVERTISING.

20:34.434 --> 20:36.544
- WELL, YOU MUST KNOW
A THING OR TWO

20:36.569 --> 20:38.639
ABOUT SCREWING PEOPLE
YOURSELF.

20:38.671 --> 20:40.611
- YEAH, I COULD DO IT
IN MY SLEEP.

20:40.640 --> 20:42.680
- I BET YOU COULD.

20:42.709 --> 20:45.009
- YOU KNOW, DAVE,

20:45.044 --> 20:47.884
WHAT'S WEIRD ABOUT YOU
MEETING MIKEY...

20:47.914 --> 20:48.824
- "MIKEY"?

20:48.848 --> 20:51.978
- IS THAT WE USUALLY MEET GUYS
TOGETHER.

20:52.018 --> 20:55.458
- AND THEY USUALLY END UP
WITH YOU.

20:55.488 --> 20:57.558
- THE LUCKY ONES.

20:57.590 --> 21:00.490
- DEBATABLE.

21:00.527 --> 21:05.427
- SO WHAT'D I MISS?
- NOTHING SPECIAL.

21:05.465 --> 21:14.335
*

21:14.374 --> 21:15.644
- OKAY.

21:15.675 --> 21:18.805
IDENTIFY MY FAVORITE ARIA
OF ALL TIME,

21:18.845 --> 21:21.075
AND YOU INSTANTLY BECOME
MY NEW FAVORITE PERSON.

21:21.113 --> 21:23.883
- OH, WELL, THANKS FOR NOT
