21:23.916 --> 21:27.916
[laughs]

21:27.954 --> 21:30.424
[La Clemenza di Tito
playing on CD player]

21:30.457 --> 21:31.917
CLEMENZA DI TITO,

21:31.958 --> 21:34.658
SESTO'S ARIA, ACT TWO.

21:34.694 --> 21:36.334
