21:36.363 --> 21:38.933
- OKAY, STOP TRYING TO MAKE ME
FALL FOR YOU.

21:38.965 --> 21:40.665
[both laugh]
- WHO'S TRYING?

21:40.700 --> 21:42.000
- YOU ARE THE FIRST PERSON

21:42.034 --> 21:44.544
I'VE MET IN PITTSBURGH
WHO KNOWS SESTO'S ARIA.

21:44.571 --> 21:46.811
- I'M THE ONLY OTHER PERSON
WHO KNOWS.

21:46.839 --> 21:49.579
- YOU KNOW, WHEN I WAS A KID,

21:49.609 --> 21:52.909
I USED TO PRETEND I WAS SICK
ON SATURDAY AFTERNOONS

21:52.945 --> 21:54.005
SO I COULD SKIP LITTLE LEAGUE

21:54.046 --> 21:56.616
AND LISTEN TO THE MET OPERA
BROADCASTS ON THE RADIO.

21:56.649 --> 21:57.879
- I WISH I'D KNOWN YOU.

21:57.917 --> 22:02.117
WE COULD'VE LISTENED TOGETHER.

22:02.154 --> 22:07.864
*

22:07.894 --> 22:10.564
