22:10.597 --> 22:13.067
- [softly]
YEAH.

22:13.099 --> 22:16.099
ONLY, UH...

22:16.135 --> 22:19.565
I'M NOT QUITE READY YET.

22:19.606 --> 22:21.106
- IT'S OKAY.

22:21.140 --> 22:23.040
- BUT I WILL BE SOON.

22:23.075 --> 22:25.905
AND, UH...

22:25.945 --> 22:28.045
I HAVE A FEELING
IT'S GOING TO BE GREAT.

22:28.080 --> 22:36.020
*

22:41.628 --> 22:43.598
- YOU HAD A HIDEOUS TIME,
