22:43.630 --> 22:45.000
- [laughs]

22:45.031 --> 22:47.671
AH, I DON'T MIND GOING OUT
ONCE IN A WHILE.

22:47.700 --> 22:49.740
- ARE YOU IMPLYING
THAT I'M A SCENE QUEEN?

22:49.769 --> 22:51.739
- YOU ARE A SCENE QUEEN.

22:51.771 --> 22:53.871
- WE'RE IN PITTSBURGH.
THERE IS NO SCENE.

22:53.906 --> 22:55.876
- YEAH, SO WHAT'S
THE BIG ATTRACTION?

22:55.908 --> 22:57.738
- WELL, IF YOU DON'T GO OUT,
YOU DON'T MEET PEOPLE.

22:57.777 --> 23:00.177
- YOU MET ME.
- RARE EXCEPTION.

23:00.212 --> 23:02.012
BESIDES, MY FRIENDS ARE HERE.
- YOUR FRIENDS?

23:02.048 --> 23:03.178
SOME FRIENDS.

23:03.215 --> 23:05.015
YOUR FRIEND BRIAN
TRIED TO HIT ON ME.

23:05.051 --> 23:06.151
- HE DID NOT.

23:06.185 --> 23:07.945
- I'VE BEEN AROUND THE BLOCK.

23:07.987 --> 23:10.887
- HE'S ALWAYS LIKE THAT.
BESIDES, HE WAS HIGH.

23:10.923 --> 23:13.033
- I'M JUST TELLING YOU.
- HE WOULDN'T.

23:13.059 --> 23:15.059
- HE DID.

23:17.464 --> 23:19.634
- SHIT.

23:19.666 --> 23:21.196
WELL, HE CAN'T HAVE YOU.

23:21.233 --> 23:23.603
YOU'RE MINE.

23:32.512 --> 23:34.452
- WHOO!

23:42.922 --> 23:45.592
- I TOLD YOU,
I'M NOT GOING.

23:45.625 --> 23:47.525
- I PROMISED HIM
YOU'D BE THERE.

23:47.560 --> 23:50.060
- WELL, YOU SHOULD STOP MAKING
PROMISES THAT I CAN'T KEEP.

23:50.096 --> 23:51.656
- HEY, DON'T BE A SHIT.

23:51.698 --> 23:53.628
