RID OF HIM.

23:57.737 --> 24:00.167
- TELL IT TO THE JUDGE.

24:00.206 --> 24:03.606
- WHEN DID YOU START SOUNDING
LIKE YOUR GIRLFRIEND?

24:03.643 --> 24:06.553
- IT'S TIME YOU BECAME PART
