OF SOME COMMUNITY.

24:11.518 --> 24:13.088
AND IT DOESN'T MEAN
I HAVE ANYTHING IN COMMON

24:13.119 --> 24:15.049
WITH SOMEONE ELSE WHO DOES.

24:15.087 --> 24:15.887
- YOU KNOW,
IT'S MORE THAN THAT.

24:15.922 --> 24:18.092
WE NEED TO TAKE CARE
OF EACH OTHER.

24:18.124 --> 24:20.094
- I DON'T NEED TO TAKE CARE
OF ANYONE.

24:20.126 --> 24:22.526
AND I DON'T NEED ANYONE
TO TAKE CARE OF ME.

24:22.562 --> 24:23.862
- ONE DAY YOU MIGHT.

24:23.896 --> 24:24.856
- [sighs]

24:24.897 --> 24:26.797
FUCK GROUPS.

24:26.833 --> 24:28.843
- I THOUGHT YOU DID.

24:28.868 --> 24:30.568
- OCCASIONALLY.

24:30.603 --> 24:34.773
BUT IT'S BY INVITATION ONLY.

24:36.208 --> 24:39.178
