* JUST GIVE ME
ONE MORE CHANCE *

44:22.260 --> 44:25.930
* IF YOU'RE STILL IN DOUBT

44:25.964 --> 44:28.304
* BABY, WALK AWAY

44:28.333 --> 44:33.743
* ONE MORE DANCE
IF WE WORK IT OUT *

44:33.772 --> 44:37.112
