44:43.481 --> 44:45.281
- I DON'T THINK SO.

44:45.316 --> 44:47.986
- WELL, WHAT DO YOU WANT TO DO?

44:48.019 --> 44:50.859
- TAKE YOU HOME.

44:54.760 --> 44:58.460
- * JUST GIVE ME
