45:15.914 --> 45:20.754
- [laughs]

45:20.786 --> 45:23.986
- CAPTAIN ASTRO.

45:51.950 --> 45:55.050
- WHO ARE YOU THINKING ABOUT?

45:55.086 --> 45:57.916
- WHAT?

